  <text xml:lang="ta">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="Aink93-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">muyakkam peṟṟavaḻip piṟanta veṟi nāṟṟattāl paṇṭaiyaḷavaṉṟi vaṇṭukaḷ
          moyttaṉavāka, ‘itaṟkuk kāraṇam eṉ’ eṉṟu viṉāviya cevilittāykkuk kūṟuvāḷ pōṉṟu talaimakaṉ
          ciṟaipuṟattāṉākat tōḻi colliyatu.
        </p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>
      <div xml:id="Aink93">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l>erumainal lēṟṟiṉa mēya larunteṉap</l>
          <l>pacumō rōṭamō ṭāmpa lollā</l>
          <l>ceyta viṉaiya maṉṟa palpoḻiṟ</l>
          <l>ṟātuṇ veṟukkaiya vākiyivaḷ</l>
          <l>pōtaviḻ mucci yūtum vaṇṭē.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">

<l>           The bees, rejecting white lotus and green Catechu plants, </l> 
<l rend="indent2">           because those have [already] been fed on </l> 
<l rend="indent4">           by the herds of good buffalo bulls as they grazed,  </l> 
<l>         are ones whose work has truly already been done [for them]: </l> 
<p/>
<l>         They feed themselves on the crown of this girl's head, </l> 
<l>         on its opening flower buds, </l> 
<l>         and thus become rich by eating pollen from many groves. </l> 


        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
